{"tid":124729,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法官陳慶偉指斥鄭錦滿：「唔好係法庭玩手機，你嚟呢度做咩？」","createTime":"2017-02-18T00:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T15:13:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"34caab961c40b22c2be78ba599c2be7a54ec40c6","tid":124729,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T00:33:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56315884&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170217\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56315884%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170217&d=ciqixHjE7SQ%2Bh8bl84MOe5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=2cf65bc5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56315884%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170217&h=e3638151\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56315884&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170217</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s28.postimg.org/98micquel/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs28.postimg.org%2F98micquel%2Fimage.jpg&h=119e1868&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n17名佔旺人士因於佔旺清場當日未有離開，前年遭律政司控告刑事藐視法庭，案件今在高院處理，其中被告「四眼哥哥」鄭錦滿及歐煜鈞認罪。鄭錦滿今遲了到庭，及後當資深大狀麥高義替他進行求情時，鄭坐在旁聽席上玩手機，結果被法官質疑其認罪誠意。<br />\n<br />\n法官陳慶偉指斥鄭錦滿：「唔好玩手機，你嚟呢度做咩？唔係你鍾意嚟就嚟，玩就玩，點睇倒你係有誠意道歉？」<br />\n<br />\n麥高義亦承認鄭的行為不尊重法庭，透露鄭差少許便可完成大學學位，亦承認案發時鄭背後有政治組織。鄭於庭外透露認罪是因為不想再跟對方糾纏，希望盡快完結這事。<br />\n<br />\n鄭於2014年11月佔旺清場當天，被警方拍得臉戴口罩、手持黃色橫額於示威區出現。"},{"pid":"fe56e4fd15d27936dda6ed253faadd2a9250ae5e","tid":124729,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T00:35:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>麥高義亦承認鄭的行為不尊重法庭，透露鄭差少許便可完成大學學位</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條撚樣去澳洲咁多年仲乜的?<br />\n<br />\n英文屎到死, 讀又讀唔成 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" cla